      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition. The engine and transmission are operational, though the car shows significant signs of wear consistent with its age. The interior has visible staining and wear on the upholstery, and the exterior has several noticeable scratches and minor dents. All major electronic systems are functioning, but some secondary features may require attention.",
