    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You've honestly got to see this beauty in person. It's in absolutely stunning shape, seriously like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've pampered this car since day one, and it drives like a total dream. If you're looking for that perfect, 'good as new' feel without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message, I'd love to show it to you!",
      "price": 43900.0,
