    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade A80 Supra Turbo, retaining its original 2JZ-GTE power plant and Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission. This example features untouched factory sequential turbochargers and the original helical limited-slip differential. The chassis exhibits zero torsional fatigue, with all factory spot welds intact and a flawless undercarriage. Mechanical integrity is verified by consistent compression across all six cylinders and a leak-down test with minimal variance. The double-wishbone suspension retains all OEM bushings in prime condition, ensuring precise lateral geometry and damping. Finished in original Renaissance Red with a pristine interior, this is a true investment-grade specimen of Japanese grand touring engineering.",
